 <h1>Kauai Dining Guide for Vegetarians</h1>
 
    <div id="mainContentSection">
     <!--  TEXT_COLUMN start -->
<p>This list of dining options on Kauai is to help Hindu pilgrims keep a pure vegetarian diet. Restaurants range from pure vegan and vegetarian where no meat, fish or eggs are ever used in the kitchen at any time, to those that offer excellent vegetarian fare along side a regular "steak and lobster" menu. Others do not cater specifically to vegetarians at all, but serve a wide range of fresh vegy options. Last on the list are "limited vegy options," These restaurants have excellent views and facilities, but be prepared to work with your waiter to design your meal. Listings are sorted by level of offerings and proximity  to the temple.</p>


<p>Disclaimer: Not all proprietors communicate changes to us, web addresses, descriptions of cuisine, etc., may change.  Try to Google the location to get updated info and please send notification that such-and-such a dining  info is invalid, to <a href="mailto:iraivan@hindu.org">iraivan@hindu.org<a/></p>
