<p><b>Description: </b>This is a recently opened Wailua location of Kalaheo's very popular and original Brick Oven Pizza. They offer a vegetarian pizza, a vegetarian sandwich and salad options. Sandwiches less than $6.70; pizzas $9-$29  Still makes pizza the old fashioned way. Brick Oven is the quintessential mom-and-pop business. The pizza is cooked directly on the brick hearth, brushed with garlic butter, and topped with cheeses and long-simmering sauces. This is the real thing! You have a choice of whole-wheat or white crust, plus many toppings:  vegetarian combos, and more. The result: very popular pizza, particularly when topped with fresh garlic. The  pizza-bread sandwiches are big at lunch, and the "super pizza" with everything on it -- that's amore.</p>
